thread.title: Jacqueline Olaman
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Jacqueline Olaman

author: Jacqueline Olaman
title: Jacqueline Olaman
text: I have used Omega before and each time have found them to be reliable. We picked up and dropped off the car at Wellington Airport. All pick up and drop off instructions were as described. I had to use a car seat (free) for a toddler and had asked for the harness to be put through the top slots as in my car at home. This was done and I was able to pop the tired toddler straight into his seat with no adjustments needed. Thankyou. Would not hesitate to use Omega again.
